title: Tyreek Hill | Ep 150 | ALL THE SMOKE Full Episode | SHOWTIME Basketball

description:
The NFL is BACK tonight and so is ATS with another big-time football guest. Matt and Stak are joined by new Dolphins star receiver Tyreek Hill. The former Chiefs star opens up about his trade to Miami, the difference between Tua Tagovailoa & Patrick Mahomes, and his expectations for the squad this season. Plus, he talks about his time in Kansas City and their Super Bowl run in 2020.
